HEADWORD: Dinornis
<hw>Di*nor"nis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr.
<?/ terrible + <?/ bird.]</ety> <fld>(Paleon.)</fld> <def>A genus of
extinct, ostrichlike birds of gigantic size, which formerly inhabited
